- Players should not insert more than one creadit at a time. Continues are prohibited;
- Players will have 40 minutes of practice (they can restart the game at will during this period) and a final run after it.
- If a player manages to clear a loop within the first 40 minutes, they can opt to stop playing and use it as their final score. If they decide to continue playing, the score from the clear will be invalidated;
- The only score to be considered will always be the last one achieved by the player.
- If by some miracle (or curse) two players finish their runs with the exact same score, the tiebreaker will be: fewest bombs used > how far they made it in the game.",,"A browser to share the game screen through VDO.Ninja.
